name: MarBeth Dunn
what_you_do: Ten Million for World Peace is a mission-driven initiative that aims to gather 10 million individuals to meditate for world peace, focusing on creating a unified field of consciousness to influence world leaders towards peace and harmony.
who_you_serve: The initiative serves individuals interested in meditation and world peace, as well as spiritual seekers and community members who wish to participate in collective healing practices.
signature_programs: Master Healing Circle, Monthly Meditation for World Peace
current_projects: February Energy Reset Ritual, Monthly Meditation for World Peace, Weekly 'Imagine Peace' Podcast
bio: Co-founders MarBeth Dunn and Teri Angel are recognized spiritual teachers.
